name: Trolltunga
description:
Back in 2018 I took a solo trip to Norway with a single and almost unreachable (to me) goal.. to complete one of the most spectacular hikes: Trolltunga (troll´s tongue).Trolltunga is the most scenic and spectacular cliffs in Norway, hovering 700 metres above Ringedalsvatnet lake. The hike through high-mountain terrain up to Trolltunga (1180 m) is long and demanding, but you are rewarded with magnificent views. 
Took me 12 hours to complete, right after this, and still in Norway, I started photographing people, until present day.
